A data set containing environmental condition of an Abies species

abies

Format

A tibble object with 5000 rows and 10 variables:

ID

presence and absences records ID

pr_ab

presence and absences denoted by 1 and 0 respectively

x y

columns with coordinates

from column aet to landform

columns with environmental variables

...
